name: The Fear of Being Judged
description:
Our dependence on what others think of us becomes overwhelming at times. As if the whole world is judging our every word, every action, every creation... with the "judges" being wicked and ruthless. They're waiting for us to make a mistake and this hellish experience becomes more and more unbearable.
This art is what it feels like.
It is also inside our heads and is never real, remember that.
